-- Tronox Wins Court Approval of Its Disclosure Statement to Exit Bankruptcy
-- B y   T h o m   W e i d l i c h   a n d   T i f f a n y   K a r y
-- 2010-09-23T19:24:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-23/tronox-wins-court-approval-of-its-disclosure-statement-to-exit-bankruptcy.html
Tronox Inc., a bankrupt chemical
maker, won court approval of its disclosure statement explaining
the terms of its plan to exit bankruptcy protection.  U.S. Bankruptcy Judge Allan Gropper in New York approved
the disclosure statement at a hearing today.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Thom Weidlich in New York at 
 tweidlich@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
